OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mostly cloudy day with
OL,6,Foccasional outbreaks of light rain.
OL,7,FThe rain will be mainly across the
OL,8,Fwest. Drier in the east with some
OL,9,Fbrighter spells. Brisk westerly winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThis evening will be cloudy
OL,12,Fwith a few outbreaks of rain. Then the
OL,13,Frest of the night will be cloudy with
OL,14,Foccasional rain in the west, mainly
OL,15,Fdry in east.
OL,16,
OL,17,CTuesday:FA little patchy rain at
OL,18,Ffirst, otherwise dry and mostly
OL,19,Fcloudy. Some brighter spells in the
OL,20,Feast where it will be warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
